IN RE the MARRIAGE OF Angela Sue TETER and Clarence Wayne Teter Upon the Petition of Angela Sue Teter, Petitioner-Appellee, And Concerning Clarence Wayne Teter, Respondent-Appellant. No. 18-0302 Court of Appeals of Iowa. Filed December 19, 2018

DECISION WITHOUT PUBLISHED OPINION

Clarence Teter appeals the district court decision denying his motion to modify spousal support. REVERSED IN PART AND REMANDED.

REVERSED IN PART. REMANDED.
